    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in truly mint, showroom condition and represents a rare find for a discerning buyer. The exterior paint is flawless with a deep, mirror-like finish, and the body is entirely free of any dents, scratches, or imperfections. Inside, the cabin remains in pristine state, with the upholstery and trim showing no signs of wear, still retaining that new-car feel. Mechanically, it is perfect, having been meticulously maintained and stored in a climate-controlled environment. You can expect a vehicle that looks and drives as if it just rolled off the assembly line.",
